  "bio_raw": "Prior joining to ULAB, Mr. Sakib has five years of fulltime teaching experience in Canadian University of Bangladesh and Primeasia University. He also worked as adjunct faculty at leading private universities of Bangladesh like North South University and East West University.\nIn addition to that, he had been accoladed with several academic administrative positions like Director of Career Counselling & Placement Cell (CCPC) of CUB and Director of BBA & MBA programs of PAU.\nFurthermore, he has one-year industry experience at Standard Chartered Bank.",
